sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    participant user

    Note right of user: User writes a new note

    user->>browser: Writes note in text field and clicks Save
    activate browser
    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Confirmation of note creation
    deactivate server
    deactivate browser

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated notes list including the new note
    deactivate server
